{
  "stem": "12289.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, of course, we-- we had to put everything aside, just for doing one thing, namely to support and help the Raoul Wallenberg mission.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So everyone was, more or less-- the girls were typing, writing, sending code telegrams to Sweden and all that and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we-- we were helping to negotiate with the-- the Hungarian government about these passports.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a supporting role in that-- on that respect, and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I would say that the whole-- the whole staff were, more or less, engaged in this work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, they were printed in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a big operation there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, it was sad enough that even other people managed to illegally print this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there were, towards the end of the war, many, many false passports circulating, printed by some organizations who I don't know really, really who they were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was a fact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came in hands of the Nazis, and also, which-- which, of course, sometimes they blame Raoul Wallenberg for having given the Nazi people their passports, which, of course, never happened.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- but this-- this is-- was a very, very difficult situation, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I told you, I-- I stayed in the house owned by Manfred Weiss, a Jewish industrialist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He and his family then, later on, managed to-- to buy themselves out from-- That's the only group I know of who managed to-- to escape with-- after negotiating with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But anyhow, that's beside the point, just now, because in this house was a distant relative of Manfred Weiss, also, and his wife living.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had breakfast with them, every morning, there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, they didn't turn up.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
